  "message": "chore: add MCP agent configuration files for multi-tool development\n\nAdd MCP (Model Context Protocol) configuration files for the various\ncoding agent tools used in development of this project. These enable\neach tool to connect to the agent-mail coordination server and other\nMCP services consistently.\n\nFiles added: cline.mcp.json, codex.mcp.json, cursor.mcp.json,\nfactory.mcp.json, gemini.mcp.json, opencode.json, windsurf.mcp.json\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
